{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_018B7kNZue3YdArKzFhP5w56","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014e2nHnBYTjk3US1j6PTmJi","name":"mcp__plat__comment","input":{"owner":"plat","name":"timealign-initial","number":5,"body":"## Summary\n\nReworked the UI into a single **content-first, Wikipedia-style design system** (`src/ui.ts`) and rebuilt the homepage, game board, and 404 on it. All four review follow-ups are addressed:\n\n1. **Shared auth chip** — now a reusable component in the body header on every page, including the 404 (was previously missing there).\n2. **Timeline container** — the game board timeline lives in its own rectangular bordered box, so its width is stable as it grows.\n3. **Substantial simplification** — two fonts (Linux Libertine for titles, Helvetica elsewhere), all text black except hyperlink blue, no custom colours / borders / all-caps. The one functional exception (transient green/red placement feedback) is retained and noted.\n4. **Body header** — Wikipedia-style: two thin rules at content width with left/right-aligned utility info. The page header is now just the title (*Timelines Demo*) + back arrow.\n\nGame engine untouched; README updated to match.\n\n## How it was verified\n\n`lint` / `typecheck` / `build` all pass; CI `check` green. Drove the live preview with Playwright:\n\n- **Homepage** — minimal page header, body header between two rules, catalogue infobox + `wikitable` picker render correctly.\n- **Game board** — played a round: placed *Hiroshima* after the Titanic anchor → Commit revealed *August 6, 1945*, Score 100 · Streak 1, next card dealt; timeline grows inside its container without shifting width.\n- **404** — auth chip now renders in the body header (*Sign in* while signed out); puzzle id HTML-escaped.\n- **Console** — only pre-existing benign noise (anonymous `/api/me` 401, missing favicon).\n\n### Next steps\n\n- [Persist scores + leaderboard](https://git.plat.local/plat/timealign-initial/issues/new?title=Persist%20scores%20and%20add%20a%20per-puzzle%20leaderboard&body=Save%20completed-puzzle%20results%20to%20Postgres%20via%20a%20src%2Fmigrate.ts%20migration%20and%20surface%20a%20per-puzzle%20best%20and%20recent-scores%20panel%2C%20tied%20to%20the%20existing%20Forgejo%20SSO%20identity.%20Add%20the%20%60agent-work%60%20label%20to%20this%20issue%20to%20have%20an%20agent%20build%20it.)\n- [Custom puzzle builder](https://git.plat.local/plat/timealign-initial/issues/new?title=Add%20a%20custom%20puzzle%20builder&body=Add%20a%20page%20to%20author%20a%20new%20puzzle%20%28events%2C%20dates%2C%20summaries%2C%20tags%29%20validated%20live%20against%20the%20typed%20%60Puzzle%60%20schema%2C%20producing%20a%20shareable%20%2Fplay%20link.%20Add%20the%20%60agent-work%60%20label%20to%20this%20issue%20to%20have%20an%20agent%20build%20it.)\n- [Auto-source puzzles from Wikidata & Wikipedia](https://git.plat.local/plat/timealign-initial/issues/new?title=Auto-source%20puzzles%20from%20Wikidata%20and%20Wikipedia&body=Generate%20puzzles%20on%20demand%20for%20any%20era%20or%20topic%20by%20querying%20Wikidata%2FWikipedia%2C%20emitting%20them%20against%20the%20existing%20typed%20%60Puzzle%60%20contract%20the%20API%20already%20exposes.%20Add%20the%20%60agent-work%60%20label%20to%20this%20issue%20to%20have%20an%20agent%20build%20it.)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":274,"cache_read_input_tokens":70242,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":274},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ea97c4a2-67f7-4ff7-8c74-f9bccb4cced2","uuid":"73d63429-ca28-4bb3-a9fb-d4daf455e9d1","request_id":"req_011Cc8qtYquz86gRmzNDS9aQ"}
